rows.label: tev015701_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Dart about recent developments.

rows.label: tev015701_MSG0001
rows.name:
You see all these materials lying around?
Steel frames and whatnot?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG0002
rows.name:
I told my Mediator brother Beats over there to get all
this crap outta the way.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG0003
rows.name:
But he said we can't spare any people for large-scale
maintenance projects yet, so we're just gonna leave 'em
lying around.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG0004
rows.name:
If it wasn't for these things, we could have big parties
here every night. What a waste![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG0008
rows.name: Is Gerome eating at Army Pizza AGAIN?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG0009
rows.name:
He's always talking about beating up xenoforms,
but if he's going to scarf down pizza every day,
he ain't gonna beat up anyone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG0010
rows.name:
Well, if my boss ain't going on a mission, looks like
I'm free to screw around the rest of the day. Niiiice.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG0020
rows.name:
They talk all shy, and yet they have all this crazy tech.
And I don't think they understand they're just a bunch
of New LA freeloaders![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG0021
rows.name: We're gonna have to teach 'em our rules.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG0022
rows.name:
You wanna rat on 'em to the Mediators?
If so, my brother Beats is standing guard over there.
...If you call that slouching "standing guard."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG0023
rows.name:
Aw, who am I kidding? You're too big of a deal to be
wasting your time on getting a few Ma-non in line.
Now hurry up and wreck the Ganglion already![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG0030
rows.name:
Gerome needed to vent some of his anger issues,
so we went and knocked out a quick bounty mission.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG0031
rows.name:
But during the fight, I tore off a simius's arm and it
got all enraged on us![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG0032
rows.name:
Damn thing ended up putting one of my team in the
Mimeosome Maintenance Center.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG0033
rows.name:
Goddammit! Why'd we have to land on such a
flaming turd of a planet?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG0046
rows.name:
Heh heh heh. Looks like Gerome finally stopped
screwing around.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG0047
rows.name:
Now he can go burn off all that anger that's been
eating at him since the Ma-non took over Army Pizza.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG0048
rows.name:
Ah, but don't get me wrong. I don't wanna be starting
a war with 'em or nothing.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG1049
rows.name:
I totaled my brand-new Skell, and they said it'll cost
me 80 large to salvage it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG1050
rows.name:
Well, I went postal when they told me that.
Started screaming about how no honest man has
that kind of scratch.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG1051
rows.name:
But then, my brother Beats stepped up and said that
he'd pay the salvage fee for me![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG1052
rows.name:
What the hell, man? He's always complaining about
how crappy the division rewards are for Mediators,
and then he goes and does that?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG1053
rows.name:
What an idiot. ...Still, I guess I'd better take on a big
mission so I can get some cash and buy him a nice
steak dinner.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG1060
rows.name:
I can't believe that douchebag at the pizza place
tried to frame Gerome.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG1061
rows.name:
Things got so bad there, I was worried that the
Ma-non might retaliate against us humans.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG1062
rows.name:
Instead they're all "Um, so so so now we can't get our
usual pizza anymore, right?" ...And that was it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev015701_MSG1063
rows.name:
I can't believe how forgiving they are!
...Or maybe they're just complete morons.[ST:wait ]
